{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/pulls/10760", "id": 10420072, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MTA0MjAwNzI=", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/10760", "diff_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/10760.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/10760.patch", "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10760", "number": 10760, "state": "closed", "locked": false, "title": "more useful rustpkg init", "user": {"login": "minhnhdo", "id": 705015, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcwNTAxNQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/705015?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo", "html_url": "https://github.com/minhnhdo", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "body": "This PR modifies the behavior of `rustpkg init`.\n\n`rustpkg init` now accepts two more arguments, the first is the type of package to initialize (`bin` or `lib`), and the second is the package name. Instead of initializing a workspace in the current directory, `rustpkg init` now initializes a workspace under the directory with the same name as the supplied package name. In addition, it also creates some default crates (i.e. `lib.rs` or `main.rs`) under `src/<package-name>/`.\n\nE.g. `rustpkg init lib awesome_lib` will create the following directory tree in the current directory.\n\n```\nawesome_lib/ \n - bin/\n - build/\n - lib/\n - src/\n    - awesome_lib/\n       - lib.rs\n```\n\nThe content of `lib.rs` is the following.\n\n``` rust\npub fn get_answer() -> int {\n    42\n}\n```\n\nEDIT: `test.rs` is no longer generated.\nPS: re-opening of #10651, as per request @alexcrichton\n", "created_at": "2013-12-02T01:52:32Z", "updated_at": "2014-07-16T02:00:15Z", "closed_at": "2014-01-08T16:08:21Z", "merged_at": null, "merge_commit_sha": "76a164913feddaa87796d68eb69287d1385cc4d2", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/pulls/10760/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/pulls/10760/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10760/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/statuses/109bd7173f67a5bcee3748c8c0b01f931a1406be", "head": {"label": "minhnhdo:rustpkg-init", "ref": "rustpkg-init", "sha": "109bd7173f67a5bcee3748c8c0b01f931a1406be", "user": {"login": "minhnhdo", "id": 705015, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcwNTAxNQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/705015?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo", "html_url": "https://github.com/minhnhdo", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/minhnhdo/re